%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20didn't%20see%20much%20of%20Disney%20World%20at%20night%20because%20our%20kids%20got%20tired.%3Cp%3EChris%20Thomas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrick%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Get%20an%20early%20flight%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20your%20vacation%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-things-to-do-at-disney-world-someone-with-annual-pass-2021%5C%22%3Emaximize%20your%20time%20at%20Disney%20World%20parks%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20a%205%20a.m.%20flight%20to%20Orlando%2C%20stopped%20by%20our%20resort%20to%20drop%20off%20our%20bags%2C%20and%20got%20to%20the%20parks%20before%20noon.%20I%20really%20thought%20we'd%20won%20this%20one%20...%20but%20it%20all%20fell%20apart%20shortly%20before%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kids%20got%20cranky.%20They%20were%20exhausted%2C%20not%20only%20from%20walking%20around%20the%20park%20all%20day%20in%20the%20sun%2C%20but%20also%20from%20being%20awoken%20from%20their%20slumber%20at%203%3A30%20a.m.%20to%20go%20to%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ended%20up%20going%20back%20to%20the%20resort%20much%20earlier%20than%20anticipated%2C%20missing%20all%20of%20the%20nighttime%20fun%2C%20including%20the%20fireworks.%20This%20trick%20might%20be%20better%20suited%20for%20teens%20or%20adults.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPlanning%20the%20trip%20on%20my%20own%20didn't%20save%20me%20money%20or%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrick%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Skip%20the%20travel%20planner%20and%20book%20a%20trip%20on%20your%20own%20so%20it's%20personalized%20and%20as%20affordable%20as%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20always%20been%20a%20do-it-myself%20type%20of%20travel%20planner.%20And%20not%20to%20brag%2C%20but%20I%20nailed%20it%20on%20our%20first%20trip%20to%20Disney.%20Everything%20went%20great%2C%20and%20my%20family%20had%20a%20fabulous%20time.%20But%20looking%20back%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure%20%3Cem%3EI%3C%2Fem%3E%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20great%20memories%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20a%20vacation%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20a%20quest%20to%20get%20the%20best%20deals%2C%20the%20right%20reservations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgetting-popular-dining-reservations-at-disney-world-restaurants-best-tips-2022-4%5C%22%3Ethe%20perfect%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20least%20it%20was%20cheaper%20than%20hiring%20a%20travel%20planner%2C%20right%3F%20Nope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20next%20trip%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-pack-for-disney-according-to-vacation-planner-2022-1%5C%22%3Eenlisted%20a%20Disney%20trip%20planner%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20did%20all%20of%20the%20work%20of%20making%20reservations%20and%20got%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20best%20rates%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20case%20for%20all%20travel%20planners%2C%20but%20the%20Disney%20trip%20planner%20cost%20us%20nothing.%20Since%20we%20stayed%20on%20Disney%20property%20for%20three%20nights%2C%20she%20earned%20a%20commission%20from%20Disney%20%E2%80%94%20not%20us.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20free%2C%20she%20booked%20our%20trip%20and%20answered%20questions%20throughout%20the%20entire%20vacation.%20I%20was%20way%20less%20stressed%20and%20more%20present%20with%20my%20kids%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20spend%20time%20buried%20in%20my%20phone%20figuring%20out%20the%20next%20plan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUsing%20Disney%20gift%20cards%20for%20souvenirs%20worked%20for%20most%20of%20our%20kids%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224009%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22alien%20popcorn%20bucket%20disney%20souvenir%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60a68aa5f27b4c0019445a62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222673%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20all%20know%20Disney%20isn't%20cheap.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Gritchen%2FDigital%20First%20Media%2FOrange%20County%20Register%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrick%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Give%20your%20kids%20Disney%20gift%20cards%20with%20a%20set%20amount%20so%20they%20can%20buy%20souvenirs%20while%20sticking%20to%20a%20set%20budget.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20travel%20blogs%20suggest%20buying%20your%20kids%20Disney%20gift%20cards%20before%20the%20trip%20so%20they%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-employees-what-souvenir-to-buy-2018-8%5C%22%3Euse%20a%20set%20amount%20of%20money%20to%20purchase%20souvenirs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20gift%20cards%20can%20be%20purchased%20in%20advance%20at%20stores%20like%20Target%20and%20Walmart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20giving%20your%20kids%20gift%20cards%2C%20they%20know%20exactly%20how%20much%20money%20they%20have%20to%20spend%20during%20the%20trip%2C%20and%20you%20easily%20set%20a%20budget.%20For%20a%20minute%2C%20I%20thought%20this%20one%20would%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20our%20kids%C2%A0took%20those%20gift%20cards%20down%20to%20almost%20nothing%2C%20but%20our%20third%20just%20isn't%20a%20big%20shopper%2C%20and%20he%20left%20a%20bunch%20of%20money%20on%20the%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cards%20don't%20expire%2C%20so%20technically%2C%20we%20aren't%20out%20anything%2C%20but%20now%20we%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do%20with%20this%20gift%20card%20back%20home.%20If%20this%20was%20cash%2C%20we%20could%20spend%20it%20where%20we%20wanted%2C%20but%20since%20it's%20on%20a%20card%2C%20we're%20forced%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20spend%20it%20on%20the%20Disney%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20after%20experiencing%20the%20ups%20and%20(mostly)%20downs%20of%20these%20travel%20hacks%20on%20our%20first%20adventure%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20just%20embrace%20spending%20more%20on%20our%20next%20visit%20to%20Disney%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20October%202%2C%202023%2