0model%20that%20wouldn't%20be%20loud%20and%20distracting.%20I%20found%20what%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56307-20%26h%3D86df1892d7e89b85b89f345848058b81ca2a5ea3864b1302790ca368dd4d359e%26postID%3D67212281434c477c2347c061%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fcoway-airmega-ap-1521hh-mighty-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB01728NLRG%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoway%20Airmega%20AP-1512HH%20Mighty%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20air%20purifier%20designed%20for%20medium-to-large%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20the%20Coway's%20performance%2C%20I%20conducted%20air%20quality%20tests%20using%20incense%20in%20a%20closed%20room.%20Then%2C%20I%20used%20the%20air%20purifier%20for%20several%20weeks%20in%20my%20home%2C%20running%20it%20around%20the%20clock.%20The%20Coway%20was%20ahead%20of%20the%20pack%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-air-purifier%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20best%20purifiers%3C%2Fa%3E%20we've%20tested.%20Here's%20why%20we%20recommend%20the%20model%20as%20the%20top%20choice%20for%20busting%20indoor%20pollutants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8dc4fb7-274f-4f38-8634-555c54428b95%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Set%20up%20and%20design%5C%22%3ESet%20up%20and%20design%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20the%20Coway%20Airmega%20AP-1512HH%20Mighty%20up%20and%20running%20took%20under%20five%20minutes.%20When%20I%20unboxed%20the%20air%20purifier%2C%20I%20found%20the%20manual%20resting%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20package.%20The%20unit%20itself%20was%20wrapped%20in%20plastic%2C%20which%20I%20removed.%20Then%2C%20following%20the%20manual's%20instructions%2C%20I%20popped%20off%20the%20front%20grill%20and%20removed%20the%20activated%20carbon%20and%20HEPA%20air%20filters%20(also%20encased%20in%20plastic)%20from%20the%20unit%2C%20replacing%20them%20after%20unpackaging%20was%20complete.%20The%20grill%20is%20easy%20to%20snap%20on%20and%20off%2C%20making%20filter%20changes%20a%20breeze.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20plugged%20the%20power%20cord%20into%20the%20unit%20and%20an%20electrical%20outlet%2C%20and%20it%20was%20good%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20carbon%20filter%2C%20which%20reduces%20odors%20such%20as%20smoke%2C%20cleaning%2C%20and%20pet%20odors%2C%20and%20the%20HEPA%20filter%2C%20which%20filters%20microscopic%20airborne%20particles%20like%20bacteria%20and%20viruses%2C%20the%20Airmega%20contains%20a%20washable%20prefilter.%20It%20prevents%20larger%20particles%20like%20dust%2C%20lint%2C%20and%20pet%20hair%20from%20clogging%20the%20other%20filters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22top%20down%20look%20of%20the%20Coway%20airmighty%20mega%20%20to%20see%20controls%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6721491da0a0cc14f224c74e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Coway%20Airmega%20AP-1512HH%20Mighty%20control%20panel%2C%20on%20top%20of%20the%20unit%2C%20displays%20the%20indoor%20air%20quaility%20in%20real%20time.%3Cp%3EHeidi%20Borst%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Airmega%2C%20which%20comes%20in%20black%20or%20white%2C%20has%20five%20fan%20speed%20settings%3A%20low%2C%20medium%2C%20high%2C%20auto%2C%20and%20Eco.%20These%20settings%20are%20located%20on%20a%20control%20panel%20on%20top%20of%20the%20unit%2C%20and%20I%20found%20them%20easy%20to%20access%20and%20adjust.%20The%20air%20purifier%20also%20contains%20an%20ionizer%2C%20but%20we%20advise%20turning%20off%20the%20ionization%20function.%20That's%20because%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Findoor-air-quality-iaq%2Fwhat-are-ionizers-and-other-ozone-generating-air-cleaners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%20(EPA)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ionizers%20typically%20produce%20ozone%2C%20a%20harmful%20lung%20irritant%2C%20as%20a%20byproduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Coway%20is%20designed%20so%20that%20air%20enters%20the%20filtration%20system%20at%20the%20front%20of%20the%20unit%20rather%20than%20the%20back%2C%20with%20filtered%20air%20exiting%20at%20the%20top%2C%20which%20enables%20you%20to%20place%20the%20unit%20on%20top%20of%20a%20table%20or%20close%20to%20a%20wall%20without%20impairing%20its%20function.%20I%20keep%20mine%20in%20the%20corner%20of%20my%20bedroom%20and%20hardly%20notice%20it%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Coway%20includes%20an%20air%20quality%20indicator%20light%2C%20a%20helpful%20feature%20that%20changes%20color%20as%20air%20quality%20improves%3B%20red%20signifies%20unhealthy%20VOC%20levels%2C%20purple%20means%20moderate%20VOC%20levels%2C%20and%20blue%20means%20levels%20are%20healthy.%20When%20I%20use%20a%20product%20containing%20fragrance%20in%20my%20bedroom%2C%20it%20kicks%20into%20higher%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ddf530c2-7ddc-4db1-9ff4-8a68d2b46af6%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Coway%20Airmega%20AP-1521HH%20Mighty%20%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECoway%20Airmega%20AP-1521HH%20Mighty%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223810%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Coway%20airmighty%20mega%20and%20air%20filter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6721491d9b3250dbbceaf300%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222857%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Coway%20Airmega%20AP-1512HH%20Mighty%20prefilter%20captures%20large%20particles%20like%20pet%20fur.%3Cp%3EHeidi%20Borst%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20over%2030%20models%20we%20tested%2C%20the%20Coway%20AirMega%20AP-1521HH%20Mighty%20air%20purifier%20was%20the%20fastest%20at%20removing%20volatile%20organic%20compounds%20(VOCs)%20and%20air%20pollutants%20like%2