-4d46-8503-1a2602269832%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDetails%20on%20policy%20positions%20hidden%20inside%20a%20mission%20to%20build%20housing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20to%20the%20map%20itself%20proved%20a%20challenge%20for%20a%20first-timer%20like%20me%2C%20as%20it's%20not%20part%20of%20the%20game's%20default%20and%20wildly%20popular%20multiplayer%20combat%20mode.%20A%20true%20Fortnite%20aficionado%20would've%20known%20how%20to%20use%20the%20access%20code%20online%20to%20find%20Freedom%20Town%2C%20but%20it%20took%20me%20a%20few%20minutes%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20track%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20finally%20arrived%20in%20Harris'%20Fortnite%20world%2C%20I%20was%20plopped%20into%20a%20train%20station%20that%20resembles%20the%20New%20York%20City%20subway%20or%20DC%20Metro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mission%3A%20Use%20Harris'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-small-businesses-tax-breaks-cut-red-tape-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposed%20%2450%2C000%20tax%20break%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20small%20businesses%20to%20acquire%20building%20supplies%20to%20assemble%20new%20affordable%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20went%20about%20my%20tasks%2C%20I%20noticed%20the%20map%20was%20also%20very%20public%20transit-oriented%2C%20from%20the%20subway%20station%20to%20buses%20dotting%20almost%20every%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20Fortnite%20first-timer%20like%20me%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20game%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewas%20relatively%20easy%20to%20pick%20up%2C%20although%20I%20found%20myself%20floundering%20in%20mini-games%20meant%20to%20help%20me%20collect%20construction%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20peak%2C%20I%20saw%20around%20180%20other%20gamers%20present%20on%20the%20map%20with%20me.%20They%20seemed%20to%20be%20notably%20younger.%20One%20player%20who%20remained%20unmuted%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20coughing%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20a%20real%20gamer's%20perspective%2