tion%20series%20%E2%80%9CDaredevil%3A%20Born%20Again%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CIronheart%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CWonder%20Man%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20animated%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Diego%20Ramos%20Bechara%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fdeadpool-and-wolverine-disney-plus-release-date-1236125615%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India-China%20Disengagement%20Complete%2C%20Exchange%20Of%20Sweets%20Tomorrow%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESticking%20to%20the%20announced%20timeline%2C%20India%20and%20China%20have%20completed%20disengagement%20in%20the%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20regions%20of%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20and%20patrolling%20will%20begin%20soon%2C%20said%20Army%20sources%2C%20adding%20that%20sweets%20will%20also%20be%20exchanged%20with%20troops%20from%20the%20Chinese%20side%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Diwali%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20from%20the%20Indian%20Army%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20verification%20process%20is%20on%20and%20the%20modalities%20of%20patrolling%20will%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20ground%20commanders.%20Chinese%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Xu%20Feihong%20told%20reporters%20in%20Kolkata%20hours%20later%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20had%20reached%20%26quot%3Bmany%20important%20understandings%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20very%20important%20meeting%20between%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20(on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20in%20Russia%20last%20week).%20Now%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20have%20reached%20important%20understandings%2C%20they%20will%20be%20the%20guidelines%20for%20the%20further%20development%20of%20relations%20between%20our%20two%20countries.%20I%20hope%20that%2C%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20this%20consensus%2C%20our%20relations%20will%20be%20moving%20forward%20smoothly%20in%20the%20future%20and%20they%20will%20not%20be%20restricted%20or%20interrupted%20by%20specific%20disagreements%20between%20our%20two%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ambassador%20said.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20two%20neighbouring%20countries%2C%20it%20is%20natural%20that%20we%20have%20some%20differences%20and%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20how%20to%20handle%20and%20solve%20them.%20The%20meeting%20of%20the%20two%20leaders%20has%20set%20a%20very%20good%20example%20for%20us%20on%20how%20to%20handle%20these%20differences%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESatellite%20Images%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2021%2C%20India%20had%20announced%20that%20a%20patrolling%20agreement%20had%20been%20reached%20for%20the%20two%20contentious%20areas%20of%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20and%20the%20troops%20would%20return%20to%20the%20positions%20that%20existed%20before%20the%20stand-off%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20began%20in%202020.%20The%20disengagement%20process%20included%20the%20dismantling%20of%20structures%20and%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20land%20on%20which%20they%20stood%20to%20their%20original%20condition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20agreement%20was%20announced%2C%20NDTV%20had%20accessed%20the%20first%20satellite%20images%20proving%20that%20structures%20were%20being%20removed%20by%20the%20Chinese%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20image%20from%20the%20Depsang%20plains%20taken%20on%20October%2011%20showed%20four%20vehicles%20and%20two%20tents%20and%2C%20in%20another%20from%20October%2025%2C%20the%20tents%20were%20gone%20and%20the%20vehicles%20could%20be%20seen%20moving%20away.%20The%20images%20were%20of%20an%20area%20near%20the%20'Y%20Junction'%20from%20where%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20prevented%20from%20travelling%20east%20to%20India's%20patrolling%20points%2C%20which%20mark%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20that%20India%20claims%20in%20these%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fjvt800h_depsang-disengagement_625x300_25_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20set%20of%20images%20showed%20semi-permanent%20Chinese%20structures%20being%20removed%20from%20Demchok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EForward%20Movement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stand-off%20began%20in%20May%202020%20and%20a%20clash%20took%20place%20in%20Ladakh's%20Galwan%20the%20next%20month%20in%20which%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20action%20and%20the%20Chinese%20side%20also%20suffered%20losses%2C%20with%20the%20exact%20number%20remaining%20unconfirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20troop%20buildup%20followed%20on%20both%20sides%20and%20military-level%20talks%20began%20taking%20place%20to%20resolve%20the%20stand-off.%20In%20September%202022%2C%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20withdrew%20from%20the%20contentious%20Gogra-Hot%20Springs%20area%20in%20Ladakh%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20pre-April-2020%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20latest%20patrolling%20agreement%20was%20announced%20by%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20on%20October%2021%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwe-will-be-able-to-go-back-to-2020-patrolling-s-jaishankar-on-lac-border-row-6839082%5C%22%3Econfirmed%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20reached%20an%20agreement%20on%20patrolling%2C%20and%20we%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20the%202020%20position.%20With%20that%2C%20we%20can%20say%20the%20disengagement%20with%20China%20has%20been%20completed...%20There%20are%20areas%20which%2C%20for%20various%20reasons%20after%202020%2C%20they%20blocked%20us%2C%20