e%20cap%20of%20his%20Coke%20and%20exclaimed%3A%20%26quot%3BIs%20she%20crazy%3F%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BToo%20many%20Thank%20yous...Must%20be%2035%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fviral-video-shows-how-donald-trump-comes-up-with-his-social-media-posts%2Farticleshow%2F114780085.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fviral-video-shows-how-donald-trump-comes-up-with-his-social-media-posts%2Famp_articleshow%2F114780085.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fviral-video-shows-how-donald-trump-comes-up-with-his-social-media-posts%2Famp_articleshow%2F114780085.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MLA%20Jignesh%20Mevani%20Demands%20IAS%20Officer's%20Suspension%20Over%20'Anti-Dalit'%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Congress%20MLA%20Jignesh%20Mevani%20on%20Wednesday%20demanded%20the%20suspension%20of%20Mahisagar%20District%20Collector%20Neha%20Kumari%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20making%20anti-Dalit%20comments%2C%20a%20charge%20the%20bureaucrat%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mevani's%20demand%20comes%20a%20week%20after%20he%20sought%20similar%20action%20against%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20Rajkumar%20Pandian%20for%20allegedly%20misbehaving%20with%20him%20and%20one%20of%20his%20party%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLA%20targeted%20Kumari%20citing%20a%20purported%20video%20in%20which%20she%20was%20heard%20saying%20that%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20cases%20registered%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%20or%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%2C%20are%20used%20for%20blackmailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20termed%20the%20lawmaker's%20claims%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20unsuccessful%20attempt%20to%20get%20political%20mileage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mevani%20visited%20Lunawada%2C%20the%20district%20headquarters%2C%20and%20demanded%20that%20an%20FIR%20be%20registered%20against%20the%20collector%20under%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%20and%20that%20she%20was%20suspended%20over%20her%20%E2%80%9Cinsensitive%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunparliamentary%E2%80%9D%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20one%20Vijay%20Parmar%20went%20to%20meet%20the%20collector%20with%20his%20grievance%20at%20the%20SWAGAT%20programme%20on%20October%2023%2C%20she%20used%20%E2%80%9Cunparliamentary%E2%80%9D%20words%20against%20him%20and%20also%20insulted%20the%20lawyer%20community%20by%20saying%20they%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9Cslapped%20with%20slippers%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Vadgam%20MLA%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESWAGAT%20is%20an%20initiative%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20for%20the%20redressal%20of%20people's%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mevani%2C%20the%20collector's%20claim%20that%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20cases%20under%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%20are%20misused%20for%20blackmailing%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20SC%20and%20ST%20communities%20and%20amounts%20to%20an%20offence%20under%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%20and%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20demand%20Kumari's%20suspension%20and%20that%20a%20case%20be%20registered%20against%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20collector%20called%20the%20MLA's%20allegations%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20stunt%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20man%20whom%20the%20MLA%20called%20poor%2C%20innocent%20young%20friend%20(Vijay%20Parmar)%20has%20a%20police%20case%20against%20him%2C%20and%20his%20brother%20has%20more%20than%20one%20case%20of%20rape%2C%20kidnapping%20and%20assault%20against%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumari%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20keep%20visiting%20the%20collector's%20office%20with%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20SWAGAT%20programme%20on%20October%2023%2C%20he%20pressured%20the%20collector%20to%20file%20a%20case%20against%20police%20officers.%20When%20the%20collector%20told%20him%20that%20she%20did%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20file%20a%20case%20and%20that%20he%20should%20approach%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(SP)%20or%20the%20court%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20pester%20her%20over%20his%20issue%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20even%20threatened%20the%20officers%20and%20told%20the%20collector%20that%20she%20was%20a%20Brahmin%20and%20he%20would%20let%20her%20know%20what%20%E2%80%9Csection%204%20of%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%20entailed%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20understand%20the%20direction%20in%20which%20this%20MLA%20wants%20to%20take%20law%20and%20order%20by%20keeping%20a%20person%20with%20a%20criminal%20history%20along%20with%20him%20even%20when%20the%20state%20government%20is%20sensitive%20about%20children%20and%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collector%20said%20that%20the%20way%20Vijay%20Parmar%20is%20%E2%80%9Cblackmailing%E2%80%9D%20government%20employees%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%20is%20not%20at%20all%20right.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20MLA's%20support%20to%20such%20people%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20real%20complainants%20and%20the%20real%20victims%20to%20get%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20Dalit%20community%20members%20gathered%20outside%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Gandhinagar%20demanding%20the%20suspension%20of%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20Rajkumar%20Pandian%20over%20his%20alleged%20misbehaviour%20with%20Mevani%20and%20his%20party%20colleague.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730291400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-mla-jignesh-mevani-demands-ias-officers-suspension-over-anti-dalit-remark-6908487%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Congress%20MLA%20Jignesh%20Mevani%20on%20Wednesday%20demanded%20the%20suspension%20of%20Mahisagar%20District%20Collector%20Neha%20Kumari%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20making%20anti-Dalit%20comments%2C%20a%20charge%20the%20bureaucrat%20rejected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-mla-jignesh-mevani-demands-ias-officers-suspension-over-anti-dalit-remark-6908487%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20About%20The%20Indian-American%20Vote%20-%20What%20Issues%20Matter%20And%20Who%20They%20Prefer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20week%20from%20now%2C%20America%20will%20know%20who%20their%20next%20President%20will%20be.%20The%20contest%20between%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20been%20a%20bitter%20one%2C%20which%20has%20left%20much%20of%20the%20US%20divided%20and%20polarised.%20A%20group%20that%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20significant%20one%20is%20that%20of%20Indian-Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20than%205.2%20million-strong%20Indian-American%20community%2C%20eligible%20to%20vote%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20group%20that%20can%20potentially%20swing%20the%20election%20outcome%20towards%20either%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20second-largest%20immigrant%20group%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20Indian-American%20community%20have%20historically%20favored%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20in%20overwhelming%20numbers.%20However%2C%20the%20Republican%20Party%20has%20long%20felt%20that%20the%20community's%20votes%20are%20significant%20and%20hence%20the%20party%20has%20changed%20its%20policies%20on%20the%20economy%2C%20social%20issues%2C%20and%20stewardship%20of%20the%20US-India%20bilateral%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20election%2C%20there%20has%20been%20greater%20focus%20on%20the%20Indian-American%20community%20since%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20American%20history%2C%20a%20candidate%20of%20Indian%20heritage%20-%20Democratic%20nominee%20Kamala%20Harris%20-%20could%20occupy%20the%20highest%20office%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20people%20of%20Indian%20heritage%20play%20an%20increasingly%20important%20electoral%20role%20in%20deciding%20who%20will%20be%20the%20next%20US%20President%20and%20how%20that%20will%20shape%20America's%20future%2C%20an%20extensive%20survey%20was%20conducted%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieendowment.org%2Fresearch%2F2024%2F10%2Findian-american-voters-election-survey-us%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarnegie%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20understand%20how%20Indian-Americans%20will%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20SURVEY%2C%20THE%20FINDINGS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%2C%20conducted%20in%20partnership%20with%20research%20and%20analytics%20firm%20YouGov%2C%20finds%20that%20as%20the%20November%205%20elections%20approach%2C%20Indian-Americans%20remain%20solidly%20behind%20the%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20though%20there%20is%20an%20uptick%20in%20support%20for%20Republican%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20shows%20that%20from%20Kamala%20Harris's%20perspective%2C%20six%20out%20of%20every%20ten%20Indian-Americans%20favour%20the%20Democrats%2C%20while%20from%20Donald%20Trump's%20point%20of%20view%2C%20one%20in%20every%20three%20persons%20of%20Indian%20heritage%20is%20likely%20to%20vote%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20also%20suggests%20that%20there%20is%20a%20considerable%20gender%20factor%20to%20it%20too.%20%26quot%3BSixty-seven%20per%20cent%20of%20Indian%20American%20women%20intend%20to%20vote%20for%20Harris%20while%2053%20percent%20of%20men%2C%20a%20significantly%20smaller%20share%2C%20say%20they%20plan%20to%20vote%20for%20Harris%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20shows%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BTwenty-two%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20intend%20to%20vote%20for%20Trump%20while%20a%20significantly%20larger%20share%20of%20men%2C%2039%20percent%2C%20plan%20to%20cast%20their%20ballots%20for%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20should%20also%20come%20as%20a%20worry%20for%20Democrats%20as%20it%20shows%20that%20%26quot%3BForty-seven%20per%20cent%20of%20respondents%20identify%20as%20Democrats%2C%20down%20from%2056%20per%20cent%20in%202020.%26quot%3B%20For%20the%20same%20time%20period%2C%20the%20share%20of%20Republican%20supporters%20has%20held%20steady%20while%20the%20percentage%20of%20independents%20has%20grown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20reveals%20that%20the%20Indian%20heritage%20factor%20does%20not%20always%20work%20for%20every%20candidate.%20People%20who%20took%20the%20survey%20showed%20that%20Indian-American%20Republicans%20such%20as%20Nikki%20Haley%2C%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20and%20Usha%20Vance%20(wife%20of%20Republican%20vice%20presidential%20nominee%20JD%20Vance)%20were%20rated%20unfavorably%20by%20Indian-Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20the%20the%20research%2C%20the%20issue%20that%20was%20rated%20highest%20among%20Indian-Americans%20was%20'inflation'%20and%20'cost%20of%20living'%20which%20was%20tied%20with%20'state%20of%20the%20economy'%20and%20'jobs'%2C%20closely%20followed%20by%20'abortion%20and%20reproductive%20rights'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESURVEY%20INSIGHT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20survey%20focuses%20on%20several%20interesting%20data%20sets%20and%20reveals%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20approximately%205.2%20million%20people%20of%20Indian%20origin%20residing%20in%20the%20United%20States%20today%2C%20of%20which%203.9%20million%20are%20eighteen%20or%20older.%20According%20to%20data%20available%2C%20it%20is%20estimated%20that%20there%20are%20roughly%202.6%20million%20eligible%20Indian-American%20voters%20today.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBetween%202010%20and%202020%2C%20the%20Indian-American%20community%20has%20grown%20by%2050%20per%20cent%2C%20making%20it%20the%20second-largest%20immigrant%20community%20by%20country%20of%20origin%2C%20trailing%20only%20Mexican-Americans.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20median%20household%20income%20for%20Indian%20Americans%20is%20roughly%20%24153%2C000%2C%20more%20than%20double%20the%20figure%20for%20the%20country%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20graphs%20that%20show%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20survey%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F1ih8incc_us-election-survey-indian-americans_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fekkolqos_us-election-survey-indian-americans_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fgjsamvq8_us-election-survey-indian-americans_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%