%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parents%20Of%20Next%20Chief%20Justice%20Of%20India%20Wanted%20Him%20To%20Be%20Chartered%20Accountant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESenior%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20will%20take%20oath%20as%20the%2051st%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20on%20November%2011%2C%20but%20his%20parents%20wanted%20him%20to%20be%20a%20Charted%20Accountant.%20They%20believed%20a%20legal%20career%20was%20full%20of%20challenges%20and%20hardship%2C%20sources%20close%20to%20him%20said.%20But%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20chose%20to%20embrace%20the%20law%2C%20inspired%20by%20his%20uncle%2C%20Supreme%20Court's%20Justice%20HR%20Khanna.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BHe%20always%20considered%20his%20uncle%20an%20ideal%20and%20used%20to%20keenly%20follow%20his%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%20And%20that%20involved%20not%20only%20the%20law.%20%26quot%3BJustice%20HR%20Khanna%20used%20to%20polish%20not%20only%20his%20shoes%20but%20also%20that%20of%20other%20family%20members.%20He%20used%20to%20wash%20his%20own%20clothes%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnSanjiv%20Khanna%20has%20preserved%20all%20the%20copies%20of%20Justice%20HR%20Khanna's%20judgments%2C%20notes%2C%20registers%2C%20sources%20said.%20He%20wants%20to%20donate%20them%20to%20the%20top%20court's%20library%20once%20he%20demits%20office.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%202019%2C%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20spent%20his%20first%20day%20as%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20in%20the%20same%20court%20room%20where%20his%20uncle%20worked.%20Justice%20HR%20Khanna's%20portrait%20is%20there%20in%20the%20room%2C%20but%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20never%20got%20his%20photo%20clicked%20there.%20He%20would%20do%20so%20before%20he%20retires%2C%20sources%20said.%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20is%20expected%20to%20demit%20office%20on%2013%20May%202025.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnJustice%20Sanjeev%20Khanna's%20mother%20Saroj%20Khanna%20was%20