2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjimmy-kimmels-19-minute-monologue-for-republicans-yes-i-am-biased-against-trump%2Farticleshow%2F114778581.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjimmy-kimmels-19-minute-monologue-for-republicans-yes-i-am-biased-against-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F114778581.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjimmy-kimmels-19-minute-monologue-for-republicans-yes-i-am-biased-against-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F114778581.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rizwan%2C%20Pakistan's%20New%20ODI%20Captain%2C%20Sends%20Loud%20CT%202025%20Message%20To%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20impasse%20over%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20venue%20continues%2C%20Pakistan's%20newly%20appointed%20ODI%20and%20T20I%20skipper%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20has%20broken%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20matter.%20The%20Indian%20team%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20prompting%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20to%20demand%20alternate%20options.%20While%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20in%20Pakistan%20cricket%20are%20trying%20their%20best%20to%20prevent%20the%20tournament%20from%20being%20taken%20out%20of%20the%20country%2C%20no%20resolution%20has%20been%20achieved%20on%20the%20matter%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERizwan%2C%20who%20replaced%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Pakistan's%20new%20white-ball%20skipper%2C%20has%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFans%20here%20love%20Indian%20cricketers%2C%20and%20they%20would%20be%20thrilled%20to%20see%20the%20Indian%20team%20play%20in%20Pakistan.%20If%20they%20come%2C%20we%20will%20give%20them%20a%20warm%20welcome%2C%26quot%3B%20Rizwan%20said%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUncertainty%20continues%20to%20loom%20over%20India%20going%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20mega%20event.%20Since%202008's%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20India%20has%20not%20played%20any%20cricket%20tournaments%20in%20Pakistan%20due%20to%20tense%20relationships%20between%20both%20nations%20because%20of%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20series%20played%20from%20December%202012%20to%20January%202013%20in%20India%20marked%20the%20final%20bilateral%20series%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%20Since%20then%2C%20both%20nations%20have%20only%20clashed%20at%20ICC%20tournaments%20and%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Pakistan%20travelled%20to%20India%20on%20three%20occasions%20since%20the%202008%20Asia%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20reports%20started%20to%20surface%20about%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20looking%20at%20three%20options%20regarding%20hosting%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20ICC%20is%20either%20looking%20to%20have%20the%20tournament%20go%20ahead%20in%20Pakistan%20as%20planned%20or%20take%20place%20in%20both%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20hybrid%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20this%20hybrid%20model%2C%20matches%20for%20India%20and%20knockout%20stage%20games%20will%20take%20place%20in%20Dubai.%20The%20third%20option%20is%20the%20entire%20tournament%2C%20taking%20place%20outside%20Pakistan%2C%20with%20Dubai%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20or%20South%20Africa%20as%20possible%20hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730287920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndt