ents%20follow%20an%20Egyptian%20proposal%20for%20a%20two-day%20truce%20and%20limited%20hostage-prisoner%20exchange%20that%20Egyptian%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20said%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20later%20said%20he%20had%20not%20received%20the%20Egyptian%20proposal%20but%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bhave%20accepted%20it%20immediately%26quot%3B%20if%20it%20was%20raised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20month's%20killing%20of%20Hamas's%20leader%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20spurred%20hope%20that%20fresh%20life%20could%20be%20breathed%20into%20the%20truce%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn-person%20talks%20in%20August%20in%20Egypt%20and%20Qatar%2C%20based%20on%20an%20adjustment%20to%20an%20initial%20truce%20plan%20presented%20by%20Biden%20in%20May%2C%20broke%20up%20without%20a%20final%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20plan%20had%20sought%20to%20freeze%20fighting%20for%20an%20initial%20six%20weeks%20while%20Israeli%20hostages%20were%20exchanged%20for%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20and%20while%20humanitarian%20aid%20enters%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730286540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fffef62o_gaza_625x300_30_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-mediators-seek-short-term-truce-of-less-than-a-month-in-gaza-report-6907900%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mediators%20seeking%20a%20Gaza%20ceasefire%20are%20set%20to%20propose%20a%20truce%20of%20under%20a%20month%20to%20Palestinian%20operator%20Hamas%2C%20a%20source%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20talks%20told%20AFP%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-h