.%20He%20was%20arrested%20after%20Mumbai%20Police%20started%20investigating%20a%20threat%20message%20sent%20to%20Zeeshan%20Siddiqui's%20Bandra%20office%20on%20Friday%20evening.%20The%20message%2C%20sent%20to%20the%20MLA's%20office%20number%2C%20said%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20Zeeshan%20Siddique%20are%20in%20danger%20and%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20kill%20them%20is%20being%20plotted.%20The%20message%20added%20that%20the%20sender%20knew%20who%20wanted%20to%20kill%20them.%20Mumbai%20Police%20tracked%20down%20the%20number%20the%20message%20was%20sent%20from%20and%20arrested%20Gufran%20in%20Noida.%20He%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20Mumbai%20on%20a%20transit%20remand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2020-year-old%20has%20told%20police%20that%20he%20had%20planned%20to%20send%20another%20threat%20message%2C%20demanding%20money%20in%20exchange%20for%20information%2C%20but%20he%20was%20arrested%20before%20he%20could%20do%20so%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20He%20has%20told%20police%20that%20he%20was%20hoping%20that%20the%20message%20would%20scare%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20Zeeshan%20Siddique%20and%20at%20least%20one%20of%20them%20would%20try%20to%20contact%20him%20and%20he%20would%20manage%20to%20make%20some%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threat%20message%20was%20sent%20weeks%20after%20Zeeshan%20Siddique's%20father%2C%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20near%20the%20MLA's%20Bandra%20office.%20Jailed%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi's%20gang%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20Khan%20has%20received%20multiple%20threats%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks.%20Earlier%2C%20a%20vegetable%20seller%20from%20Jamshedpur%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20threat%20message%20that%20demanded%20the%20actor%20pay%20a%20ransom%20of%20Rs%205%20crore.%20Later%2C%20a%20message%20from%20the%20same%20number%20apologised%20for%20the%20ransom%20call%20and%20said%20it%20was%20a%20mistake.%20Another%20threat%20message%20to%20Mumbai%20traffic%20control%20today%20threatened%20that%20the%20actor%20would%20be%20killed%20unless%20he%20paid%20Rs%202%20crore%20as%20ransom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20messages%20come%20months%20after%20the%20firing%20incident%20outside%20the%20actor's%20Mumbai%20home%20in%20April.%20An%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20jailed%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi's%20gang%20was%20behind%20the%20firing.%20Salman%20Khan%20has%20in%20the%20past%20received%20death%20threats%20from%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20apparently%20due%20to%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20blackbuck%20hunting%20case%20in%20Rajasthan%20during%20the%20shooting%20of%20Hum%20Saath%20Saath%20Hain.%20The%20actor's%20security%20has%20been%20beefed%20up%20after%20the%20firing%20and%20death%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20an%20appearance%20on%20TV%20show%20Bigg%20Boss%2018%20days%20after%20Baba%20Siddique's%20murder%2C%20Salman%20Khan%20said%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20back%20on%20the%20show%2C%20but%20his%20work%20commitments%20brought%20him%20back.%20The%20actor%20said%20he%20didn't%20feel%20like%20meeting%20anyone%20because%20of%20the%20difficult%20situation%20he%20was%20going%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730283960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fa438ffh8_salman-khan-threat-_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnoida-tattoo-artist-wanted-to-scare-salman-khan-make-easy-money-sources-6907406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gufran%20Khan%2C%20the%2020-year-old%20arrested%20from%20Noida%20in%20connection%20with%20death%20threats%20to%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20MLA%20Zeeshan%20Siddique%2C%20has%20told%20police%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20scare%20them%20and%20make%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnoida-tattoo-artist-wanted-to-scare-salman-khan-make-easy-money-sources-6907406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%2