%202)%20The%20dome%20of%20the%20U.S.%20Capitol%20Building%20is%20visible%20as%20Chris%20Litchfield%20of%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20an%20activist%20with%20'Faithful%20America'%2C%20ties%20down%20a%2015-foot%20golden%20calf%20balloon%20meant%20to%20resemble%20Donald%20Trump.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20AFP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20symbolic%20move%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%20took%20the%20stage%20at%20the%20same%20place%20where%20Donald%20Trump%20told%20his%20supporters%20on%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bfight%20like%20hell%2C%26quot%3B%20shortly%20before%20they%20ransacked%20the%20US%20Capitol.%20She%20made%20her%20closing%20pitch%20to%20the%20Americans%20by%20painting%20next%20week's%20election%20as%20an%20existential%20choice%20between%20her%20presidency%2C%20which%20will%20come%20%26quot%3Bwith%20a%20to-do%20list%20full%20of%20priorities%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20American%20people%2C%20and%20the%20Trump%20Presidency%2C%20which%20will%20unleash%20%26quot%3Bchaos%20and%20division%26quot%3B.%20Aiming%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20all%20Americans%2C%20she%20asserted%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20democracy%20doesn't%20require%20us%20to%20agree%20on%20everything.%20That's%20not%20the%20American%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20like%20a%20good%20debate.%20And%20the%20fact%20that%20someone%20disagrees%20with%20us%20does%20not%20make%20them%20'the%20enemy%20from%20within.'%20They%20are%20family%2C%20neighbours%2C%20classmates%2C%20coworkers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ERallying%20Voters%20Is%20The%20Only%20Way%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20good%20pitch%2C%20but%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20those%20she%20was%20trying%20to%20address%20were%20listening.%20The%20polls%20remain%20tight%2C%20with%20neither%20side%20being%20able%20to%20deal%20a%20knockout%20punch.%20Rallying%20the%20base%2C%20therefore%2C%20remains%20the%20core%20aspiration%20of%20the%20two%20sides.%20This%20was%20evident%20in%20Donald%20Trump's%20Madison%20Square%20Garden%20rally%20earlier%20in%20the%20week%20where%20crude%20comments%20about%20his%20opponent%20were%20met%20with%20a%20receptive%20audience.%20Though%20Trump's%20speech%20was%20largely%20focused%20on%20immigration%2C%20his%20deportation%20plans%2C%20crime%2C%20the%20border%2C%20and%20the%20economy%2C%20others%20in%20the%20rally%20referred%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfloating%20island%20of%20garbage%26quot%3B%20and%20inferred%20that%20Jews%20are%20cheap%20and%20Palestinians%20are%20%26quot%3Brock-throwers%26quot%3B.%20Others%20referred%20to%20Harris%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bantichrist%26quot%3B%20and%20also%20said%20that%20Harris%20%26quot%3Band%20her%20pimp%20handlers%20will%20destroy%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20oldest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%20looks%20vulnerable%20from%20within.%20The%20institutional%20fabric%20is%20withering%20away%20and%20there%20is%20no%20leadership%20in%20sight%20that%20can%20provide%20some%20semblance%20of%20reassurance.%20What%20is%20remarkable%20is%20the%20dwindling%20faith%20of%20ordinary%20Americans%20in%20their%20nation's%20institutions.%20According%20to%20a%20recent%20survey%2C%20most%20voters%20think%20that%20Trump%20will%20not%20concede%20if%20he%20loses%20the%202024%20presidential%20election%2C%20with%20some%20of%20his%20supporters%20even%20positing%20that%20losing%20candidates%20have%20no%20obligation%20to%20do%20so.%20More%20disturbingly%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20voters%20have%20no%20confidence%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20be%20able%20to%20make%20the%20right%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%26quot%3BEnemy%20Within%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Trump%2C%20therefore%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20keep%20talking%20about%20migration%20and%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20which%20is%20resonating%20with%20a%20wide%20audience.%20He%20has%20promised%20to%20launch%20%26quot%3Bthe%20largest%20deportation%20programme%20in%20American%20history%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20been%20targeting%20the%20Biden%20administration%20for%20mismanagement%20of%20the%20economy.%20But%20insidiously%2C%20he%20also%20keeps%20talking%20about%20%26quot%3Ban%20enemy%20within%26quot%3B%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20him%2C%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%2C%20vicious%20radical-left%20machine%20that%20runs%20today's%20Democrat%20party%26quot%3B%20and%20upon%20which%20he%20will%20set%20the%20military%20if%20elected.%20This%20is%20aimed%20at%20keeping%20his%20base%20mobilised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20too%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20keep%20her%20base%20mobilised.%20In%20particular%2C%20she%20has%20focused%20on%20the%20women%20voters%20who%20are%20anxious%20about%20reproductive%20rights.%20The%20former%20first%20lady%2C%20Michelle%20Obama%2C%20reflected%20on%20this%20theme%20when%20she%20campaigned%20for%20Harris%20and%20made%20an%20impassioned%20plea%20to%20American%20voters%20%26quot%3Bnot%20to%20hand%20our%20fates%20over%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20Trump%2C%20who%20knows%20nothing%20about%20us%2C%20who%20has%20shown%20deep%20contempt%20for%20us%26quot%3B%2C%20because%20%26quot%3Ba%20vote%20for%20him%20is%20a%20vote%20against%20us%2C%20against%20our%20health%2C%20against%20our%20worth%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHarris%20And%20Biden%2C%20Biden%20And%20Harris%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20is%20struggling%20to%20emerge%20out%20of%20the%20shadow%20of%20President%20Biden%20as%20the%20challenges%20that%20Biden%20is%20facing%20continue%20to%20constrain%20Harris%20as%20well.%20It%20is%20a%20tough%20balancing%20act%20for%20the%20Vice-President.%20%26quot%3BMy%20presidency%20will%20be%20different%20because%20the%20challenges%20we%20face%20are%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20has%20underscored.%20%26quot%3BOur%20top%20priority%20as%20a%20nation%20four%20years%20ago%20was%20to%20end%20the%20pandemic%20and%20rescue%20the%20economy.%20Now%2C%20our%20biggest%20challenge%20is%20to%20lower%20costs%2C%20costs%20that%20were%20rising%20even%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20that%20are%20still%20too%20high.%26quot%3B%20It's%20not%20likely%20that%20for%20those%20who%20have%20been%20hurting%20economically%20looking%20at%20Harris%20outside%20of%20the%20Biden%20overhang%20will%20be%20that%20easy.%20Biden%20himself%20continues%20to%20intrude%20in%20his%20own%20way%3B%20a%20recent%20video%20of%20the%20President%20was%20doing%20the%20rounds%2C%20in%20which%20he%20was%20seemingly%20calling%20Trump's%20supporters%20%26quot%3Bgarbage%26quot%3B.%20Though%20the%20White%20House%20has%20clarified%20that%20he%20was%20referring%20to%20hateful%20rhetoric%20used%20against%20Puerto%20Ricans%20at%20the%20Trump%20rally%2C%20Trump%20has%20latched%20on%20to%20it%2C%20targeting%20Democrats%20for%20running%20a%20'hate%20campaign'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20world%20awaits%20the%20results%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20consequential%20elections%20in%20recent%20memory%2C%20the%20internal%20turmoil%20in%20the%20US%20reflects%20some%20long-term%20trends%20in%20the%20nation's%20politics.%20A%20highly%20polarised%2C%20inward-focused%20America%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20the%20world%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20leadership%20this%20moment%20in%20global%20politics%20demands.%20Other%20nations%2C%20including%20India%2C%20should%20be%20ready%20for%20this%20shift%20and%20for%20making%20their%20contributions%20toward%20managing%20the%20global%20turmoil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Harsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20Vice%20President%20%E2%80%93%20Studies%20and%20Foreign%20Policy%2C%20at%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20and%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730279040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F