%20a%20silent%20threat%20looms%20in%20the%20backdrop.%20Across%20agrarian%20units%20in%20Delhi%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20Indo-Gangetic%20plains%2C%20stubble%20burning%20in%20winter%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20menace%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20ripples%20into%20an%20annual%20public%20health%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECome%20October%2C%20farmers%20busy%20themselves%20reaping%20the%20grain.%20What%E2%80%99s%20left%20behind%20are%20two-foot-high%20stubble%20stalks.%20With%20only%20a%20short%20window%20before%20the%20land%20is%20prepared%20for%20the%20next%20cropping%20season%2C%20setting%20fire%20to%20the%20field%20seems%20the%20only%20viable%20solution%20to%20do%20away%20with%20the%20stubble%20for%20most%20farmers.%20But%2C%20the%20burning%20does%20not%20come%20without%20adverse%20effects%20%E2%80%94%20both%2C%20on%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20air%20quality%20and%20its%20citizens%E2%80%99%20lungs%20while%20further%20deteriorating%20the%20quality%20of%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20correlating%20air%20quality%20data%20with%20respiratory%20health%2C%20a%20study%20found%20that%20most%20farmers%20with%20compromised%20lung%20function%20were%20those%20who%20had%20been%20exposed%20to%20long%20hours%20of%20toxic%20haze.%20The%20plumes%20of%20smoke%20are%20a%20bed%20for%20gaseous%20pollutants%20%E2%80%94%20149.24%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20(CO2)%2C%20over%209%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20monoxide%20(CO)%2C%200.25%20million%20tonnes%20of%20oxides%20of%20sulphur%20(SOX)%2C%201.28%20million%20tonnes%20of%20particulate%20matter%2C%20and%200.07%20million%20tonnes%20of%20black%20carbon%2C%20to%20be%20precise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20study%20probing%20the%20culprit%20for%20the%20dipping%20winter%20AQI%20(air%20quality%20index)%20of%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20region%20discovered%20that%20a%20statistically%20significant%20half%20of%20particulate%20matter%20is%20contributed%20by%20burning%20crop%20residues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-b