0Mumbai%20resident%20unlearn%20and%20understand%20himself%20on%20a%20deeper%20level.%20During%20his%20eight-month%20break%2C%20Nikhil%20sought%20to%20find%20purpose%20in%20life.%20He%20loved%20teaching%20and%20interacting%20with%20young%20people%2C%20while%20his%20skills%20lay%20in%20entertainment%20and%20writing.%20How%20could%20he%20combine%20the%20two%20to%20create%20a%20tangible%20impact%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20youngsters%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pursuit%20to%20answer%20this%20question%20led%20to%20the%20launch%20of%20Yuvaa%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYuvaa%20is%20a%20purpose-driven%20youth%20media%2C%20research%2C%20and%20impact%20organisation%20that%20hopes%20to%20start%20meaningful%20conversations%20among%20India%E2%80%99s%20youth%2C%20particularly%20Gen%20Z.%20We%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20young%20people%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%20who%20are%20feeling%20lonely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20began%20with%20a%20roadshow%2C%20travelling%20to%20150%20campuses%20in%2035%20cities%20over%20nine%20months.%20The%20idea%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20to%20talk%20about%20mental%20health%20and%20sexual%20health%2C%20providing%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20young%20people%20to%20share%20their%20stories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20roadshow%2C%20Nikhil%20encountered%20many%20young%20boys%20whose%20stories%20moved%20him%20deeply.%20%E2%80%9CAn%2018-year-old%20boy%20told%20me%20that%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20told%20him%20%E2%80%98I%20love%20you.%E2%80%99%20Another%20teen%20shared%20that%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20hugged%20him.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20intimacy%20to%20our%20boys%20and%20tell%20them%20it%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332810%2Fkota-suicides-iit-jee-neet-coaching-classes-entrance-exams-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eokay%20to%20express%20themselves%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20wanted%20to%20provide%20a%20sp