%3D%5C%22577%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKumbi%20students%20spread%20awareness%20of%20waste%20segregation%20during%20one%20of%20their%20Sunday%20Campaigns.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(children)%20are%20the%20future%20of%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Indrakumar%20says%2C%20explaining%20how%20he%20overcomes%20fatigue%20despite%20the%20difficulties%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20I%20can%20bring%20some%20positive%20change%20to%20my%20society.%20The%20rewards%20education%20brings%20can%20change%20lives%20forever.%20Just%20thinking%20about%20this%20makes%20me%20happy.%20It%20drives%20me%20to%20do%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20unwavering%20dedication%2C%20Indrakumar%20inspires%20not%20only%20his%20students%20but%20also%20the%20entire%20community%20to%20envision%20a%20future%20where%20every%20child%20has%20the%20opportunity%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FEducation%2FSupport-Indrakumar%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDonate%20Now%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20By%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%3A%20Khangembam%20Indrakumar%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729662093000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D371649%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20heart%20of%20Kumbi%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Khangembam%20Indrakumar%20Singh%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20transforming%20education%20for%20underprivileged%20students.%20By%20establishing%20a%20hostel%2C%20offering%20innovative%20Sunday%20lessons%2C%20and%20championing%20environmental%20awareness%2C%20he%20empowers%20first-generation%20learners%20to%20thrive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arunava%20Banerjee%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Conservationists%20Who%20Have%20Dedicated%20Their%20Lives%20to%20Protecting%20Snow%20Leopards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fwildlife-biodiversity%2Findia-has-718-snow-leopards-most-of-them-live-in-unprotected-areas-centre-94174%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoint%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20other%20non-profit%20organisations%20on%2030%20January%202024%2C%20there%20are%20just%20718%20snow%20leopards%20in%20India%2C%20of%20which%20only%20a%20third%20are%20under%20legal%20protection.%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EStatus%20Report%20of%20Snow%20Leopards%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%20that%20barely%2034%25%20of%20the%201%2C20%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20of%20snow%20leopard%20habitat%20in%20India%20is%20legally%20protected.%20Less%20than%2070%25%20of%20this%20predator%E2%80%99s%20habitat%20remains%20unprotected.%20%3Cem%3E(Above%20images%20of%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20a%20snow%20leopard%20%26amp%3B%20Charudutt%20Mishra)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20figures%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20for%20local%20communities%20to%20be%20engaged%20in%20the%20conservation%20of%20this%20threatened%20species.%20Here%20are%20eight%20conservationists%20who%20have%20done%20incredible%20work%20in%20not%20only%20understanding%20snow%20leopards%20but%20also%20engaging%20local%20communities%20to%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECharudutt%20Mishra%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharudutt%20Mishra%20(Charu)%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%2C%20is%20considered%20by%20many%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20expert%20on%20snow%20leopard%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846