5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-264391%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKarma%20Sonam%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20worked%20for%20Karma%20is%20his%20natural%20ability%20to%20build%20and%20maintain%20close%20relationships%20with%20different%20communities.%20Leveraging%20these%20close%20relationships%2C%20he%20convinces%20and%20incentivises%20local%20communities%20to%20work%20for%20wildlife%20conservation.%20For%20decades%2C%20pastoralists%20in%20Ladakh%20have%20had%20a%20difficult%20relationship%20with%20predators%2C%20like%20snow%20leopards%20and%20wolves%2C%20who%20prey%20on%20their%20livestock.%20Through%20his%20extensive%20grassroots%20efforts%2C%20he%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20to%20repair%20that%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKoustubh%20Sharma%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoustubh%20Sharma%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Conservation%20Science%20Director%20at%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%20%E2%80%94%20has%20worked%20in%20some%20of%20the%20remotest%20and%20roughest%20terrains%20in%20the%20world%20to%20better%20understand%20snow%20leopard%20ecology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntroduced%20to%20them%20by%20Dr%20Raghu%20Chundawat%2C%20a%20pioneer%20of%20snow%20leopard%20studies%20in%20India%2C%20Koustubh%20has%20dedicated%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20time%20to%20the%20Global%20Snow%20Leopard%20and%20Ecosystem%20Protection%20Programme.%20The%20programme%2C%20according%20to%20Koustubh%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbrings%20together%20governments%20from%2012%20snow%20leopard%20range%20countries%2C%20policymakers%2C%20institutions%2C%20organisations%20and%20conservationists%20toward%20securing%20the%20future%20of%20snow%20leopards%20and%20their%20mountains%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905.jpg%3Fresize%3D1080%252C855%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905.jpg%3Fw%3D1080%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C238%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C396%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C608%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C119%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371719%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20wish%20more%20people%20knew%20about%20conservation%20initiatives%20is%20that%20not%20a%20single%20penny%20of%20the%20money%20meant%20for%20snow%20leopard%20conservation%20goes%20into%20the%20pocket%20of%20the%20snow%20leopards.%20It%20is%20always%20invested%20in%20support%20of%20people%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20local%20or%20indigenous%20communities%20running%20conservation%20programmes%2C%20the%20frontline%20rangers%20patrolling%20and%20monitoring%20wildlife%2C%20or%20the%20conservation%20teams%20working%20under%20expedition%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Koustubh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6our%20initiatives%20are%20about%20much%20more%20than%20just%20protecting%20a%20single%20species.%20We%20work%20closely%20with%20local%20and%20indigenous%20communities%20to%20create%20sustainable%20livelihoods%20that%20benefit%20both%20people%20and%20wildlife.%20When%20we%20invest%20in%20conservation%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20investing%20in%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanctuarynaturefoundation.org%2Farticle%2Fmeet-koustubh-sharma%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanctuary%20Nature%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsnowleopard.org%2Fmeet-snow-leopard-trusts-new-conservation-science-director-dr-koustubh-sharma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EShiv%20Kumar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20evening%20in%202019%20when%20Shiv%20Kumar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Deputy%20Range%20Officer%20at%20Lahaul%20forest%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20first%20spotted%20a%20snow%20leopard.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F274641%2Fforest-guard-officer-photographs-snow-leopard-conservation-himachal-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20he%20called%20it%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunforgettable%20moment%E2%80%9D.%20Thereafter%2C%20Shiv%20began%20conservation%20awareness%20classes%20about%20snow%20leopards%20among%20school%20children%20for%20the%20animal%E2%80%99s%20protection.%20He%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20villagers%20to%20inform%20them%20about%20its%20importance%2C%20threatened%20existence%20and%20its%20need%20for%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20livestock%20belonging%20to%20the%20Gaddi%20community%20%E2%80%94%20a%20community%20of%20migratory%20shepherds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20locals%20in%20the%20Lahaul%20area%20remain%20under%20threat%20from%20snow%20leopards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000